挖掘路堑可以用人力[[锹|锹]]挖、[[平地机|平地机]]、{{tsl|en|Wheel tractor-scraper|铲运机}}、[[挖掘机|挖掘机]]、[[钻爆法|钻爆法]]。<ref>Herbert L. Nichols, Jr., and David A. Day, P.E., ''Moving the Earth: The Workbook of Excavation,'' 5th ed. (New York: McGraw-Hill, 2005), pp. 8.16 et seq.</ref> 

路堑可分为山边绕过的与穿山而过的两种。<ref>Nichols and Day, ''Moving the Earth,'' p. 8.16.</ref>
 
